        {
            "title": "澳大利亞ASM計畫年底前敲定美國稀土廠選址 正與五角大樓磋商資助事宜",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> Australian Strategic Materials Ltd計畫在今年年底前為其擬建的美國稀土工廠確定選址，在美中競爭加劇之際借力於美國總統唐納德·川普對該行業的支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ASM執行長Rowena Smith周五在接受彭博電視採訪時表示，該公司一直在同美國五角大樓磋商，如何為在美國建廠生產稀土磁鐵所需金屬提供資金支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ASM目前在韓國已運營一家金屬加工廠，並希望在澳大利亞的礦產資源地建造一座礦山。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2847b7b3-6b47-3356-b98f-1b4e6f25d7fd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ASM本周股價下跌了約三分之一，但今年以來其股價仍上漲了近100%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Australian Rare Earths Firm to Select US Plant Site By Year-End</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Andy Clarke、Avril Hong、Annabelle Droulers.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9Easm%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A8%80%E5%9C%9F%E5%BB%A0%E9%81%B8%E5%9D%80-%E6%AD%A3%E8%88%87%E4%BA%94%E8%A7%92%E5%A4%A7%E6%A8%93%E7%A3%8B%E5%95%86%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C-033341099.html",
